-- Colin Keatinge
-- 2010-07-30T05:39:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/disney-announces-sale-of-miramax-films-to-filmyard-for-over-660-million.html

          
          
             Walt Disney Co. reported the sale of
Miramax Films to Filmyard Holdings LLC for over $660 million
subject to certain adjustments.  
          
          


  


        